name: TifOseMix
description:
New Merged checkpoint announced：

DuelComicMix | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

[ Tifa + Marie rose + OthersMix= TifOseMix]

推荐模型 Recommended mode
>>LuckyStrikeMix

不需要触发词，但是手部很容易畸形，可能出现猫耳\电子耳\机械结构\异色瞳等特征...（源自Shuvi休比的Lora）

Dont need trigger words.

[Known Issues]:

The hand is easily deformed, and may have features such as cat ear /electronic ear/ mechanical structure/ heterochromatic pupil (Elements From Lora of Shuvi Huby)

这个Lora是通过使用SuperMerge插件，融合了不同的Lora模型而制成的。使用到的Lora模型列表如下：

This Lora is made by using the SuperMerge plug-in and integrating different Lora models. The list of Lora models used is as follows:


Shuvi (休比- 未发布unrelased\自制selfmade）

marie rose（少女感）

Tifa_meenow（改善休比玛丽融后，五官偏下的问题+风格相似+超高质量）

RussianDollLikeness（加了一点，提供欧美特征）

JapaneseDollLikeness（加了一点，修正脸型）

小豚豚鼠（大大提升俏皮程度）

因为不同模型融合时的dimension不同，所以会有32和64的版本，不同版本大小不一致外，效果也会有所差别。另外根据是否使用SuperMerge插件的"same to strength"选项，又派生出两个版本，所以一共有4个版本。
比较不出最好效果的版本，所以全部上传了。

Because the dimensions of different models are different when merging, there will be 32 and 64 versions. In addition to the different sizes of different versions, the effect will also be different. In addition, two versions are derived based on whether to use the "same to strength" option of the SuperMerge plug-in, so there are four versions in total. I can't figure out the best version, so I uploaded it all.
